    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Culture of the the Semitic tribe or nation that is, according to tradition, descended from Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob. In modern usage, it refers to the culture of the Israelites.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
